Package: live-build
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, debootstrap | cdebootstrap | cdebootstrap-static
Recommends: cpio, gettext-base, gnu-fdisk
Suggests:
 dosfstools, genisoimage, memtest86+ | memtest86, mtools, parted,
